---
import { getRelativeLocaleUrl } from 'astro:i18n';
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import LangSwitcher from '../../components/LangSwitcher.astro';

const locale = 'en';
const homeUrl = getRelativeLocaleUrl(locale, '/');
const legalUrl = getRelativeLocaleUrl(locale, '/legal/');
---

<BaseLayout
  locale={locale}
  variant="legal"
  title="Privacy Policy | Hitorigoto Lab"
  noindex={true}
  showFooter={false}
>
  <Nav href={homeUrl}>
    ← Hitorigoto Lab
    <LangSwitcher slot="end" locale={locale} />
  </Nav>

  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: 2026-07-13 · Effective: 2026-07-13</em></p>

  <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
  <p>
    This service is operated by <strong>Hitorigoto Lab</strong> (sole proprietor: Taichi Naganuma), based in Japan.
    You can contact us by email at <a href="mailto:bookstore1308@gmail.com">bookstore1308@gmail.com</a>. We operate as an
    individual business and do not publish a postal address; please reach us by email (our address is disclosed without
    delay upon request — see our <a href={legalUrl}>Commercial disclosure</a>). Where an EU/UK representative is
    appointed (§9), their contact will be listed here.
  </p>
  <p>
    For purchases, <strong>Lemon Squeezy, LLC is the Merchant of Record (seller of record)</strong> and handles your
    payment and billing information (see lemonsqueezy.com/privacy). We do not store your card details.
  </p>

  <h2>2. What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email address</strong> — when you join a waitlist, use a free tool, or subscribe (with your consent).</li>
    <li>
      <strong>Usage / analytics data</strong> — pages viewed, referrer, coarse region, via
      <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> (cookieless, privacy-first — no cross-site tracking). Essential cookies only.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Order / fulfillment data</strong> — product purchased and delivery status (payment &amp; billing handled by Lemon Squeezy).</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not collect special-category data, and we do not sell your personal data.</p>

  <h2>3. Why we use it &amp; legal basis (GDPR Art. 6)</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Purpose</th><th>Data</th><th>Lawful basis</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Send the product / updates you requested</td><td>email</td><td>Consent — Art. 6(1)(a)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Deliver a purchased product</td><td>order data</td><td>Contract — Art. 6(1)(b)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Improve the service (analytics)</td><td>aggregate usage</td><td>Legitimate interest (cookieless, aggregate)</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>4. Cookies &amp; tracking</h2>
  <p>
    We use essential cookies only. Our analytics (Cloudflare Web Analytics) is cookieless, so no analytics consent banner
    is required. If we later add any non-essential cookies, we will ask for your consent (EU/UK) first.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Who we share with (processors)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Lemon Squeezy, LLC</strong> — payments &amp; tax (Merchant of Record).</li>
    <li><strong>Resend</strong> — sending transactional &amp; subscription email.</li>
    <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting, CDN, and cookieless analytics.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Each operates under a Data Processing Agreement (DPA). We do not sell or rent your data.</p>

  <h2>6. International transfers</h2>
  <p>
    We are based in Japan; your data may be processed outside the EEA/UK. Where required we rely on appropriate safeguards
    (e.g., Standard Contractual Clauses or provider safeguards).
  </p>

  <h2>7. Your rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>EU / UK (GDPR / UK-GDPR):</strong> access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, objection, and withdraw consent at any time.</li>
    <li><strong>California (CCPA/CPRA):</strong> know, delete, correct, and opt out of “sale/share” (we do not sell or share).</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    To exercise any right, email <a href="mailto:bookstore1308@gmail.com">bookstore1308@gmail.com</a>. We respond within
    one month (GDPR). You may also complain to your local supervisory authority.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Retention</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> kept while you are subscribed. After you unsubscribe or withdraw consent, we keep only a minimal suppression record (so we do not contact you again) and delete the rest.</li>
    <li><strong>Account / order records:</strong> until account closure, or 1 year from your last purchase (billing/tax records are retained by Lemon Squeezy as Merchant of Record).</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> aggregate, cookieless — no personal data is stored.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>9. Contact &amp; representatives</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Contact: <a href="mailto:bookstore1308@gmail.com">bookstore1308@gmail.com</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>EU representative (GDPR Art. 27):</strong> being appointed through a representative service; their name and EU address will be listed here once arranged.</li>
    <li><strong>UK representative (UK-GDPR Art. 27):</strong> likewise being appointed; contact to be listed here.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>10. Governing law</h2>
  <p>
    This policy is governed by the laws of Japan. This does not remove the mandatory data-protection rights available to
    EU / UK / California residents under their local law, which apply regardless. Your purchase contract is with Lemon
    Squeezy as Merchant of Record and is governed by their terms.
  </p>

  <h2>11. Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy; the “Last updated” date shows the latest version.</p>
</BaseLayout>
